title: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
headline: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
subtitle: Budonk-adonk! Head Tattoo
content:
Your gift of the Budonk-adonk! head tattoo for selling drugs on the street on three separate days will be available at any Tattoo Parlor before March 10.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon.
